headline.main: Warriors Will Navigate a 'Bizarre' Schedule to San Antonio

lead_paragraph: Japanese authorities confirmed Monday that all nine people aboard a rescue helicopter that crashed in snow-covered mountains in central Japan have been pronounced dead.
